body.raw:
import LinksDemo from '../../src/components/LinksDemo';

## Links in Markdown

Internal link [Go to homepage](/)

External link [Go to Google](https://google.com)

Anchor link [Go to H2 title](#h2-title)

---

## Image as external link

[![Photo by Anita Chong on Unsplash](/images/anita-chong-unsplash.jpg)](https://unsplash.com/photos/aSJAalMXCvI)

> Photo by [Anita Chong](https://unsplash.com/@jacutanita) on [Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/photos/aSJAalMXCvI)

---

## Render MDX component (with a links inside)

<LinksDemo />
